{"tid":1134844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国遊客行飛鵝山 報稱遭狼群包圍","createTime":"2019-05-02T02:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T10:25:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":257,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"a83f6fa1acc0cb6be9cd442db2d760b71f64bf2a","tid":1134844,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190502/_2019050208521014708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190502%2F_2019050208521014708.jpg&h=1bfbab91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3名內地男子來港行山，途經飛鵝山基維爾營附近時，報稱遭4隻疑似狼的動物包圍，報警求救。警方經調查並無發現。<br />\n<br />\n事發在昨晚9時許，一名22歲姓王的內地男子，聯同兩名內地友人前往麥理浩徑第5段行夜山，途經飛鵝山基維爾營附近時，有4隻疑似狼的動物在草叢內徘徊，將3人包圍。王擔心有危險，於是報警，警員趕至現場時，動物已經自行離去，警員在附近一帶搜索，並無發現狼蹤。<br />\n<br />\n3人並無受傷，由警員陪同下山。案件列作雜項處理。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，2012年曾有行山人士途經上址時，報稱遇到體形龐大的動物，警員到場發現屬巨犬品種的俄羅斯高加索犬，兇猛無比但對主人忠誠度高，市面售價逾萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1491484/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1491484%2F&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmR0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=853fdf69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1491484%2F&h=b0b9b1eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1491484/</a>"},{"pid":"13bebf1d2171316408051e77c023ab72580ade02","tid":1134844,"uid":66324,"like":387,"dislike":1,"score":386,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:55:41.000Z","msg":"係咪搞鳩d村屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749650f22586033a6ea849556deeaefa33d4e995","tid":1134844,"uid":122134,"like":193,"dislike":1,"score":192,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:56:04.000Z","msg":"狼來了"},{"pid":"29c7a2c09d87d1ffa04f610af717b9057ba3fc5e","tid":1134844,"uid":184679,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2